snippet.textDisplay:
I am extremely disappointed with Coke Studio's deliberate effort for not recognizing the original singers of this amazing song.
This song was originally composed and sung by Sanwan Faqeer and Marvi in Seraiki. It aired on Sindh TV. 
Sahir Ali Bagga has changed some lyrics and the soul of the song to make it look like a Punjabi song. But I request to the listneres to listen the original which is far more better than this.
